data.description: Welcome to your new sanctuary! This charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom home boasts an additional convenient office space/craft room, providing versatility for remote work or personal projects. With hardwood floors and laminate flooring throughout, complemented by tile in the bathrooms, this residence exudes warmth and durability. Situated on a coveted corner lot, enjoy ample space and enhanced curb appeal. Retreat to the privacy-fenced backyard, complete with a storage building for your convenience. Plus, indulge in the luxury of RV parking, catering to your adventurous spirit. Experience the perfect blend of space, functionality, and privacy in this exceptional home.
